<instruct>
/ inputdevice = keyboard
</instruct>

<page intro>
<h1>Welcome!</h1><hr>

You will be studying a series of 'one-block' and 'two-block' trials, in which each block consists of four words
that are presented one after the other for 1 second each.<br><br>
Your task is to remember the words of the <u>most recent</u> block. Thus, if the trial turns out to be a 
2-block trial, you need to forget the words of the first block and concentrate on remembering the words 
of the second block instead.<br><br>

Before each block of words is presented, you will get instructions how to read the following words: aloud or silently.<br><br>

After the final block of words in each trial, you will be presented eight 2-digit numbers and have to categorize each number to be 
smaller or larger than 50 by pressing the '<%parameters.key_smaller%>' or '<%parameters.key_larger%>' <%expressions.buttoninstruct2%>
respectively.<br><br>

<i>Each trial concludes with a cued-recall question: you will be given a category that one of the words of the
<u>most recent</u> block belonged to and are asked to enter this word  into a textbox as fast as possible.
There will only be one word that fits the category.</i><br><br>

This is a lot of information to process so let's work through two demo trials of the procedure.
</page>

<page test>
<h1>Test Start</h1><hr>
The actual test is about to start. The test will take approximately 15 minutes.<br><br>

The sequence of events for each trial is just like the ones during practice but timing will be <u>much</u> faster:<br><br>
You will only have <%parameters.distractorTaskDuration/1000%>s to categorize each number to be be smaller or larger than 50.<br>
You will only have <%parameters.cuedRecallTimeout/1000%>s to enter the recall word. <br><br>

Start when you are ready.
</page>


<text instruct1>
/ items = ("aloud")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 10.00%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ size = (80%, 8%)
/ position = (50%, 50%)
/ vjustify = center
/ txcolor = blue
</text>

<text instruct1_demo>
/ items = ("This tells you to read the following words out <u>loud</u>.<br>
Remember each word.")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 4.00%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 70%)
/ vjustify = center
/ txcolor = blue
</text>

<text instruct2>
/ items = ("silent")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 10.00%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ size = (80%, 8%)
/ position = (50%, 50%)
/ vjustify = center
/ txcolor = blue
</text>

<text instruct2_demo>
/ items = ("This tells you that another block is following.<br>
Forget the words of the first block and remember the next ones.<br><br>
Read the following words <u>silently</u>.")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 4.00%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 70%)
/ vjustify = center
/ txcolor = blue
</text>

<text distractor_demo>
/ items = ("Decide whether the number is smaller or greater than 50 and select the corresponding <%expressions.buttoninstruct2%> as fast as possible")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 4.00%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ size = (80%, 20%)
/ position = (50%, 75%)
/ vjustify = center
/ txcolor = blue
/ erase = false
</text>

<text cue_instructions>
/ items = ("Enter the word from the <u>last</u> block of 4 words that came from this category:")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 4.00%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 10%)
/ vjustify = center
/ txcolor = blue
/ erase = false
</text>

<text cue_instructionsDemo>
/ items = ("The computer will automatically convert your response to lowercase letters.")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 3.00%, true, true, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 22%)
/ vjustify = center
/ txcolor = red
/ erase = false
</text>

<text smaller>
/ items = ("<%parameters.key_smaller%>: < 50")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 8%, false, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (25%, 90%)
/ size = (30%, 8%)
/ valign = center
/ halign = center
/ erase = false
</text>

<text bigger>
/ items = ("<%parameters.key_larger%>: > 50")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 8%, false, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (75%, 90%)
/ size = (30%, 8%)
/ valign = center
/ halign = center
/ erase = false
</text>

<text finish>
/ items = ("Thank you!")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 8%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 50%)
/ size = (80%, 10%)
/ vjustify = center
/ valign = center
/ halign = center
</text>

<button exitbutton>
/ caption = "EXIT"
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 3%, false, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 80%)
/ size = (30%, 8%)
/ valign = center
/ halign = center
</button>

